title: Suriname Consumer Price Index Cpi
description: Consumer Price Index CPI in Suriname increased to 495.20 points in September from 479.30 points in August of 2022. Consumer Price Index CPI in Suriname averaged 201.45 points from 2016 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 495.20 points in September of 2022 and a record low of 94.30 points in April of 2016. This page provides - Suriname Consumer Price Index Cpi- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Statistics Suriname
